            <title>[LOG4J2-226] PDF table of contents misses Configuration and Layouts sections</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-226</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;PDF file is generated correctly with the text for all sections, but the table of contents misses the page numbers for sections Configuration and Layouts.&lt;br/&gt;
When opening the PDF in Acrobat reader, the left-hand menu does not have links for these two sections.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I noticed that the text for these sections is not in doxia XML files,&lt;br/&gt;
but in velocity template files (.xml.vm files). &lt;/p&gt;</description>
